Package homework

package homework
  • Class
    Description
    AddCommand
    Class AddCommand - used to add an array of documents to the specified catalog
    Catalog
    Class Catalog - has a name and an array of documents.
    CatalogManager
    Class CatalogManager - implements a few methods to use with objects of type Catalog - save, load, add and toString.
    Command
    Interface Command - is implemented by all the created commands
    Document
    Class Document - has an id, a title, a location and a map of tags has a function addTag - to be used for homework/bonus
    InvalidCatalogException
    InvalidCatalogException - extends Exception and is used to mark that a given catalog file is invalid.
    ListCommand
    Class ListCommand - used to print the documents from a given catalog
    LoadCommand
    Class LoadCommand - loads a catalog from a given file
    Main
    Class used to test the methods and classes implemented
    ReportCommand
    Class ReportCommand - generates a html report of a given catalog at a given path
    SaveCommand
    Class SaveCommand - saves the catalog to an external file in JSON format
    ViewCommand
    Class ViewCommand - shows the document's location using the native OS system application
